raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
do unlock_gallery_image(\"naomi\", \"1\")
Naomi: Hiya!
Naomi: Is this Mabel's Boyfriend?
Naomi: It's Naomi!
Naomi: img: naomi/2
Player: Hello, Naomi
Naomi: Heyy nice to finally meet you!
Naomi: I mean I know it's only been 2 days that I know Mabel but you're almost all she talks about 🤭
Player: Really? 😄
Naomi: Mhmm!
if Story.pink_heart >= 1:
	Naomi: She told me about the date you guys went on
	Naomi: She showed me the pictures and was all blushy
	Naomi: It was so adorable
	Player: Thanks 😊
else:
	Naomi: She told me she wanted to go out with you but seems like you've been busy
	Naomi: Hopefully you guys get to meet up soon!
	Player: Hope so too
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Naomi: She also says that you've been helping her build her confidence a lot
	Naomi: Keep this between us but we had a lot of girltalk and she's been trying to look a little more sexy for you 🤭
	Player: No way, wow!
else:
	Naomi: She's shy as a button and loves relying on you
	Naomi: She said she really wants to move in with her boyfriend soon and cuddle up every day with him
	Player: 😇
Naomi: Anyway I'm sure you probably know all that better than I do!
Naomi: Buuut since I went off on a slight tangent
Naomi: Did you have any questions about us?
Naomi: Me or the photography club? 😊
Naomi: I'd be happy to answer anything!
- Could I get your Social account?
	Player: Could I get your Social account?
	Naomi: Of course! 👍
	set PhoneUnlocks.reveal = \"naomi\"
	Naomi: You should get it now!
	Player: Thanks
	Naomi: Don't peep too hard!
	Naomi: Just kidding haha 😉
	- What if I do? [#Redheart]
		set Story.red_heart += 1
		Player: What if I do?
		Naomi: 😳
		Naomi: Wasn't expecting that 😏
		Player: Too much?
		Naomi: No actually
		Naomi: That's kind of hot 🤭 I do love an upfront guy
		Naomi: I'm tempted to send you a little something between us but I'm not a home wrecker ❤️
		Naomi: And I love Mabel too much
		Naomi: I'll have to know she's okay with something like that first!
		Player: Isn't Caleb your boyfriend?
		Player: Shouldn't he be okay with it too?
		Naomi: Yes! He is!
		Naomi: Though our relationship came out of a... not so nice mutual experience 😅
		Naomi: I'd be happy to talk about it with you after your visit!
		Naomi: I'm not the type to keep secrets but I also do think I'd like to get to know you a little better first
		Naomi: Hmmmm
		Naomi: There is... something I can share..
		Naomi: It's a little less personal buuut...
		Naomi: It might scratch the itch 😇
		Player: I'm listening
		Naomi: Well I do happen to have an exclusive fans account alongside my regular one
		Naomi: I might be interested in sharing it eventually 🤭
		Player: You're teasing me 😩
		Naomi: Hey you started it 😇
		Naomi: I'll remember to post something special just for you tonight then
		Naomi: We'll talk more about that later, I gotta get to this
	- Don't worry, I love Mabel too much for that
		Player: Don't worry, I love Mabel too much for that
		Naomi: That's like the cutest thing ever!
		Naomi: You two are such a lovely couple
		Naomi: I'll be sure to tell her too hehe
- I got nothing, thanks!
	Player: I got nothing, thanks!
Naomi: Oh right! The address!!
Naomi: So next to the main offices, there's a short blue building
Naomi: Ground floor, 2nd door to your right and voila!
Naomi: It should say \"Photography Club\" on the door
Naomi: Just give us a knock and someone will let you in!
Player: Oh cool! Thank you
Naomi: Looking forward to seeing you guys!
Player: See you then!
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
